N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 34.3 - Prohibitions

State Regulations

No person other than a sublicensee, licensed partner or supervising person may solicit business or otherwise act as an agent or broker in the name of any other agent or broker except as specified in section
2101
of the Insurance Law. Notes
